window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p>Are you looking for a vampire love story? Do you like suspenseful vampire romances from around the world?</p> <p>If so, then <i>The Prince, the Princess, and the Vampire Cat: A Love Story </i>is for you!</p> <p>According to an ancient Japanese legend, the soul of a cat can inhabit a human being.</p> <p>This story took place in a royal palace in medieval Japan many, many years ago.</p> <p>The main characters are the Prince and Princess of Hizen, who are very much in love.</p> <p><i>The Vampire Cat </i>was a classic stage play by by Gerard Van Etten.</p> <p>The book has been re-written as a short story, which features a twist of romance.</p>"; 
